<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 91-09-01R - Fiberglass Hood Wear</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi910901" tsitype="truck">
        <tsinumber>91-09-01R</tsinumber>
        <replace>
            <tsinumber>91-09-01</tsinumber>
        </replace>
        <tsidate>February, 1992</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>FRONT END SHEET METAL</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Fiberglass Hood Wear</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <truckmodelgroup/>

                <truckmodel>3000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>4000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>7000</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8100</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8200</truckmodel>
                <truckmodel>8300</truckmodel>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>To prevent hood wear at the hood to fender extensions and the hood to side cowl guides, the
                    following improvements have been made:
                </para>
                <seqlist>
                    <item>
                        <para>The fender extension seal was removed on 3000 and 4000 Series on October 15, 1990, and on
                            7100 and 8100 Series on February 19, 1991 (
                            <hotlnk xrefid="f9109011">Figure 1</hotlnk>).
                        </para>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                        <para>On November 14, 1991, stainless steel wear brackets were added to the inner hood (
                            <hotlnk xrefid="f9109012">Figure 2</hotlnk>).
                        </para>
                    </item>
                </seqlist>
                <figure id="f9109011" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g9109011.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 1. Fender Extension</caption>
                </figure>
                <figure id="f9109012" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/g9109012.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2. Stainless Steel Wear Bracket</caption>
                </figure>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
